        <p>The application pretty simple to use. The only component currently is a 'Charts' page where you can view line charts depicting how fast a upper level CS course fills up by day. The page is depicted below:</p>
        <br />
        <div style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">
            <img src="/img/screenshot.png" width="60%" style="border: 5px solid black;" />
